components.name: TabsComponent
components.templateData:
<p-tabs value="0">
  <p-tablist>
    @for(tab of tabs; track tab.value) {
      <p-tab [value]="tab.value">{{ tab.label }}</p-tab>
    }
  </p-tablist>
  <p-tabpanels>
      @for (tab of tabs; track tab.value) {
          <p-tabpanel [value]="tab.value">
              <ng-container 
                *ngComponentOutlet="tab.component"
              ></ng-container>
          </p-tabpanel>
      }
  </p-tabpanels>
</p-tabs>
